  "detailed_description": "<u><strong>Fight through randomly generated levels!</strong></u><br>Fight through multiple randomly generated levels with the help of the weapons and items you find in those levels. After fighting through all the levels you can loop through the same levels with a scaled up difficulty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/9282a440733b2ef9e74a6acd685bddbb.avif?t=1689775063\" width=608 height=342 /></span><br><br><u><strong>Equip yourself!</strong></u><br>You can equip yourself with different weapons you find or buy in the levels. You can also find different items that give you different effects depending on the item.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/8f98d9ac454dd8a200074a661e309640.poster.avif?t=1689775063\" width=608 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/8f98d9ac454dd8a200074a661e309640.webm?t=1689775063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/8f98d9ac454dd8a200074a661e309640.mp4?t=1689775063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Fight your way to victory!</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/adafb0d6f1646126f1e704d49ab118e7.poster.avif?t=1689775063\" width=608 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/adafb0d6f1646126f1e704d49ab118e7.webm?t=1689775063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/adafb0d6f1646126f1e704d49ab118e7.mp4?t=1689775063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Defeat bosses!</strong></u><br>At the end of the level you open a portal but a boss stops you before you can, each level can spawn different bosses to make sure each run is different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979990/extras/14f20c3feb85fb8a4e6266de23ab828c.avif?t=1689775063\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
